'''唐冠华''' （{{bd|1989年|7月5日|}}），男，[[山东|山东]][[青岛|青岛]]人，中国当代艺术家。<ref name="China30s.">{{cite web |url=http://en.china30s.com/?project=tang-guanhua-xingzhen-retrieve-primitive-life-experiment |title=Tang Guanhua, Xing Zhen: Retrieve Self Sufficiency Experiment |newspaper=China30s. |date=11 Jan 2018 |accessdate=2020-03-14 |archive-date=2020-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029191818/http://en.china30s.com/?project=tang-guanhua-xingzhen-retrieve-primitive-life-experiment |dead-url=no }}</ref>

由于他自愿放弃在城市的工作，并与妻子一起搬到森林里从事编织，缝纫，生态农业，可持续能源和自然建筑等自给自足生活实验，因此受到媒体的广泛采访<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/2018-04/11/c_1122663207.htm |script-title=zh:年轻夫妻在乡村建“自给自足实验室” 独立生活5年 |trans-title=Young couple builds "self-sufficiency laboratory" in the countryside and lives independently for 5 years |newspaper=XinhuaNet |language=zh |date=11 Apr 2018 |accessdate=2020-03-14 |archive-date=2020-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809120347/http://www.xinhuanet.com/2018-04/11/c_1122663207.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="The New York Times">{{cite web |url=https://sinosphere.blogs.nytimes.com/2015/06/15/living-largely-off-the-grid-in-china/ |title=Living Largely Off the Grid in China |accessdate=15 June 2015 |work=The New York Times |archive-date=2020-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919062933/https://sinosphere.blogs.nytimes.com/2015/06/15/living-largely-off-the-grid-in-china/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 他提出了一个概念，即“[[共识社区_(中国)|共识社区]]”，作为替代性社区生活的定义。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.oushinet.com/qj/qjnews/20170216/255201.html |script-title=zh:走进中国当代乌托邦 “中国共识社区”巴黎联展受瞩目 |trans-title=Entering China's Contemporary Utopia |newspaper=Nouvelles d'Europe |language=zh |date=7 Feb 2017 |accessdate=2020-03-14 |archive-date=2020-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200227150849/http://www.oushinet.com/qj/qjnews/20170216/255201.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/2018-04/11/c_1122663207.htm |script-title=zh:走入荒野：自给自足生活实验” 独立生活5年 |trans-title=Into the Wilderness: Self-Sufficiency Life Experiment |newspaper=NEWS CHINA |language=zh |date=8 Apr 2018 |accessdate=2020-03-14 |archive-date=2020-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809120347/http://www.xinhuanet.com/2018-04/11/c_1122663207.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref> 这个概念已在中国乡村振兴运动和区块链研究中被引用。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://new.qq.com/omn/20190512/20190512A0GHXL.html |script-title=zh:一人一币共识社区成立 |trans-title=One person, one coin consensus community established |newspaper=NEWS CHINA |language=zh |date=8 Apr 2018 |accessdate=2020-03-14 |archive-date=2020-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200227150842/https://new.qq.com/omn/20190512/20190512A0GHXL.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.jinse.com/bitcoin/223536.html |script-title=zh:Fitchain：区块链+健身 打造全球健身共识社区 |trans-title=Fitchain: Blockchain + Fitness Create a global fitness consensus community |newspaper=Jinse.com |language=zh |date=6 Aug 2018 |accessdate=2020-03-14 |archive-date=2020-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200227162400/https://www.jinse.com/bitcoin/223536.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 生平 ==
唐冠华于1989年出生于山东青岛。他16岁就离开了学校，开始了自己的设计业务。17岁那年，他到香港和澳门旅行时，亲眼目睹了人们如何受到资本主义和工业化的强烈影响。回大陆后，唐冠华开始深刻反思人与人之间相互伤害的现代社会结构。然后，他开始从事当代艺术领域的工作。<ref name="#1">{{cite news |url=https://echowyt1992.wixsite.com/echopage/tang-guan-hua |script-title=zh:唐冠华的家园计划 |trans-title=Tang Guanhua's Porject AnotherLand |newspaper=Echo Wang's Page |language=zh |date=2019 |accessdate=2020-03-14 |archive-date=2020-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200227150841/https://echowyt1992.wixsite.com/echopage/tang-guan-hua |dead-url=no }}</ref>

